request.description:
### Update Activity Status

This endpoint is used to update the status of a specific activity.

#### Request

- Method: PATCH

- URL: `http://localhost:3001/actividades/2/estado`

- { "estado": 2}


#### Response

The response for this request can be documented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "titulo": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "fecha": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "cupoMaximo": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "estado": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "estudiantes": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "integer"
          },
          "cedula": {
            "type": "integer"
          },
          "nombre": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "correo": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "programa": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "semestre": {
            "type": "integer"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

